beer.beer_description:
Welcome to the next level.

This indulgent Red IPA brewed using Columbus and Vic Secret hops is all about balance. With a sweet caramel malt base and dank resinous undertones that create a perfect platform to help the aromas of candied pineapples and lemons lighten up.

So hit the action button and get started.

You've earned it.
